-\n| 2017 ||\"Bloom\"||{{lang|zh-Hant|\u76db\u958b}}||''[[Game of Hunting]] OST''||\n|}\n\n===Other appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n!English title\n! Chinese title \n! Notes\n|-\n|2017\n| \"At This Moment\" ||\u5728\u6b64\u523b ||  Performance for [[CCTV New Year's Gala]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/z/v/2017-01-27/doc-ifxzyxmt1416910.shtml|title=\u80e1\u6b4c\u738b\u51ef\u5408\u4f53\u300a\u5728\u6b64\u523b\u300b \u9ed8\u5951\u4e92\u52a8\u8d85\u9017\u8da3|date=January 27, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Bibliography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable \n|-\n!  Year\n! English title\n! Chinese title \n! Notes\n|-\n|2006\n| ''Scavenger of Happiness''\n|{{lang|zh|\u5e78\u798f\u7684\u62fe\u8352\u8005}}\n|\n|}\n\n==Endorsements and Ambassadorship==\nFollowing his surge in popularity and public awareness, Hu has also been appointed the Shanghai Tourism Ambassador in 2015.<ref>{{cite news|title=The new face of Shanghai|work=[[China Daily]]|url=http://usa.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2016-01/09/content_23002016.htm|date=9 January 2016|accessdate=24 July 2018}}</ref> Professional designers from [[Madame Tussauds Shanghai]] took measurements from Hu to make two wax figures of him; one of himself and one of his character Mei Changsu from ''Nirvana in Fire'', which was unveiled in September 2016.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.shanghaidaily.com/metro/entertainment-and-culture/City-toursim-ambassador-Hu-Ges-wax-figure-unveiled/shdaily.shtml|title=City tourism ambassador Hu Ge's wax figure unveiled|website=[[Shanghai Daily]]|date=16 September 2016|accessdate=16 February 2017}}</ref>\n \nIn 2016, Hu Ge was named brand ambassador of [[Emporio Armani]] in China and Asia Pacific.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mens-folio.com/23665/hu-ge-new-face-emporio-armani-china-asia-pacific/#goRJEI76vjIh3R42.97|title=Hu Ge: The new face of Emporio Armani in China and Asia Pacific|website=Men's Folio|date=17 January 2017|accessdate=16 February 2017}}</ref> In the same year, he also became brand ambassadors for [[Piaget SA|Piaget]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://int.piaget.com/events/hu-ge-polo-s|title=Hu Ge Polo S Game Changer|website=Piaget|accessdate=1 March 2017}}</ref> [[Chanel]] Perfume and Cosmetics,<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.toodaylab.com/73304|script-title=zh:\u80e1\u6b4c\u6210\u4e3a CHANEL \u9999\u6c34\u548c\u7f8e\u5bb9\u54c1\u5f62\u8c61\u5927\u4f7f|date=15 November 2016|accessdate=1 March 2017|language=zh|trans-title=Hu Ge becomes Chanel Perfume and Cosmetics Brand Ambassador|website=Today Lab}}</ref> and [[EF Education First]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://finance.qq.com/a/20160723/012938.htm|script-title=zh:\u82f1\u5b5a\u6559\u80b2\u5f62\u8c61\u5927\u4f7f\u542f\u52a8\u82f1\u8bed\u5b66\u4e60\u65b0\u6d6a\u6f6e|date=23 July 2016|website=Tencent Finance|url-status=live|access-date=17 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n!Ref.\n|- \n|colspan=6|<center>'''Major awards</center>\n|-  \n|2011\n|  31st [[Hundred Flowers Awards]]\n| Best New Actor\n| ''[[1911 (film)|1911]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref name=juemin /> \n|-\n|rowspan=3|2015 \n| 21st [[Shanghai Television Festival]]\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| ''Forty Nine Days: Memorial''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref name=fiesta />\n|-\n| 30th [[Flying Apsaras Awards]]\n| [[Flying Apsaras Award for Outstanding Actor|Best Actor]]\n| ''[[The Disguiser]]'', ''[[Nirvana in Fire]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yule.sohu.com/20151223/n432338642.shtml|script-title=zh:\u7b2c\u4e09\u5341\u5c4a\u98de\u5929\u5956\u516c\u5e03\u63d0\u540d\u540d\u5355 \u80e1\u6b4c\u9648\u5b9d\u56fd\u4e89\u89c6\u5e1d|website=[[Sohu]]|date=23 December 2015|accessdate=27 February 2017|language=zh}}</ref>\n|- \n| 22nd [[Shanghai Television Festival]]\n| [[Magnolia Award for Best Actor in a Television Series|Best Actor]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Nirvana in Fire]]'' \n|{{won}}\n|<ref name=magnolia /> \n|