-forbes-china-celebrity-list-full-list/|title=2017 Forbes China Celebrity List (Full List)|website=Forbes|date=22 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|2019\n|3rd\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/2019-08-20/doc-ihytcitn0545378.shtml|script-title=zh:\u798f\u5e03\u65af\u4e2d\u56fd\u53d1\u5e03100\u540d\u4eba\u699c \u5434\u4eac\u9ec4\u6e24\u80e1\u6b4c\u4f4d\u5217\u524d\u4e09|publisher=Sina Corp|date=20 August 2019|language=zh}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Authority control}}\n{{Golden Eagle Award (China) Best Actor}}\n{{Magnolia Award for Best Actor}}\n{{Forbes China Celebrity 100}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hu, Ge}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:21st-century Chinese male actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Shanghai]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Chinese Mandopop singers]]\n[[Category:Chinese male voice actors]]\n[[Category:Singers from Shanghai]]\n[[Category:Chinese male singers]]\n[[Category:Chinese male film actors]]\n[[Category:Chinese male television actors]]\n[[Category:Shanghai Theatre Academy alumni]]\n[[Category:Tangren Media]]\n[[Category:21st-century Chinese singers]]\n[[Category:21st-century male singers]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{for|the director of online videos|Hu Ge (director)}}\n{{Chinese name|[[Hu (surname)|Hu]]}}\n{{infobox person\n| honorific_prefix   = \n| name               = Hu Ge\n| honorific_suffix   = \n| image              = HUGE20161211BJ.jpg\n| landscape          = <!-- yes, if wide image, otherwise leave blank -->\n| alt                = <!-- descriptive text for use by speech synthesis (text-to-speech) software -->\n| caption            = Hu Ge in 2016\n| native_name        = {{nobold|\u80e1\u6b4c}}\n| native_name_lang   = zh\n| pronunciation      = \n| birth_name         = <!-- only use if different from name -->\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|df=y|1982|9|20}}\n| birth_place        = Shanghai\n| death_date         = <!-- {{Death date and